channel.title: Needing som1 to code my server :)
channel.description:
I am willing to trust any1 with my server (I will still have a copy) I want som1 to code me special attks for my server (Zaron's isle V.2) You will be the one that will get the server a week erliar (I usually wait a week to test if there are any bugs before releasing) so if any1 is kind enough to code special attks in for me (all specials, special bar ) (not the special emote thing, the actual special bar in the wepon attk changer thing)
You will not just be getting the server, but you will make me happy and glad that ppl in this community help others :)
-Zaron
